headline: Assessing Jabil (JBL) Valuation After Rising GARP Interest And Sector Expansion
summary: Jabil (JBL) has just launched a fixed income offering of fixed rate senior subordinated unsecured notes, a funding move that sits alongside its recent profile as a Growth at a Reasonable Price stock.
